{"tid":517704,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"「拜神」呢種傳統會唔會消失","createTime":"2018-01-02T14:29:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-03T03:14:59.000Z","uid":152916,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a8be4a0c6dda07590cca277101c9a41c2f0acfa7","tid":517704,"uid":152916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T14:29:48.000Z","msg":"成日都見啊媽、啊嫲嗰啲喺大時大節拜神，祈求一家人平平安安，但係問多佢哋兩句就會話我哋唔好咁多事，去到80、90後已經無乜人識得拜神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大部分都係透過占卜、星座測驗呢啲去睇自己運情，唔係話好向往拜神呢樣嘢，只係覺得呢種文化幾得意，唔想佢失傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"188a415dd4ea5b5efa7310ecc33fe4eb0343d726","tid":517704,"uid":522,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T14:33:37.000Z","msg":"當你有一日搵返自己既靈性就唔會咁講"},{"pid":"b4284eb28df7018781763864f4ddef2328bbec37","tid":517704,"uid":54046,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T14:38:15.000Z","msg":"拜神都仲有廟祝教<br />\n拜先人唔識就真係唔知點算<br />\n拜祭先人用返佢生前希望既傳式<br />\n呢個係對先人既尊重<br />\n將心比己<br />\n如果我信道教，死左都唔想人用基督教儀式拜我<br />\n相反都係"},{"pid":"537f5092eccbfe1cc5beee2e7672b248d0914d93","tid":517704,"uid":126841,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T14:43:04.000Z","msg":"唔會 <br />\n我每年都會自己去拜我爺爺<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><del>[black]爺爺我好掛住你[/black]</del></span>"},{"pid":"bc09717f6d87a108b773ac3edf6794782a83ea98","tid":517704,"uid":129506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T14:49:57.000Z","msg":"消防局有新人到就會拜神，一路傳到宜家都仲有<br />\n<br />\n應該唔會消失<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"786759b8662b1b6e5414a5acb424e0aed9e743af","tid":517704,"uid":46910,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T14:58:32.000Z","msg":"拜神咁垃圾又臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  快D消失"},{"pid":"4abd0b8fe4b78d937439fdf1448979596a4e9d38","tid":517704,"uid":152916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"537f509